the following function will list all our contexts in our workflow

``` {.commonlisp org-language="emacs-lisp" results="none"}
(org-roam-ql-search
 '(and (tags "_c") (and (not (tags "_j")) (not (tags "@zettel:_method"))))
 "contexts"
 "title")
```

we\'re getting all the context tags `_c` but excluding journal tags `_j`
